descriptionHTML:
Astro Watch Face gives more than current time. We give You elegant design with planets position, weather and battery status. It shows current position of planets and stars. Designed for round and square watches! .

Stay tuned - in a few days we will provide a professional Horoscope within the watch face!

Features v 1.0:
- current planets position
- current weather
- live watch battery status
- live phone battery status
- beautiful and unique design

It's totally free and without ads!!!
comments: Very clean and elegant. From morning till evening I still have 60% battery at the Sony Smart Watch 3 :)
Nice watch faces Works good on moto 360 gen 1, however would like to be able to change the time from 24hr to 12hr.
No planets No planets ever show on my watch. Only the time, date, battery levels, and temp. Needs fixed.
Beautiful, free, no ads, does't install unnecessary firmware on your phone!
